name: Project 1: Portfolio Page
body:
### Hosting my Udacity Projects on Github.
This is not mandatory. It's also possible to combine all project-files into one zip-file and upload this to have the project reviewed by an Udacity-coach.
But I dedcided to make it more fancy. Git and Github need to be mastered anyhow. So it's probably a good idea to use it as often as possible...
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
